competencyQuestion: Role types of (roles of) a role set

query:
PREFIX fschema: <https://w3id.org/framester/schema/>
    PREFIX pbschema: <https://w3id.org/framester/pb/schema/>
    PREFIX pbdata: <https://w3id.org/framester/pb/data/roleset/>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?roleset
    WHERE{
    ?roleset a pbschema:RoleSet .
    }
    LIMIT 200
